. di as text _n "==== Step −1: Pre-Analysis Plan ===="

==== Step −1: Pre-Analysis Plan ====

. 
. * Lalonde 不等臂 MDE: 185 treated + 429 control, α=0.05, power=0.80
. * → d ≈ 0.247, 对应 ~$1,846 (SD ≈ 7506)
. local mde_d = 0.246

. local sd_re78 = 7506.96

. local mde_dollars = `mde_d' * `sd_re78'

. di as result "PAP MDE Cohen's d = " %5.3f `mde_d' "  →  ≈ $" %8.0f `mde_dolla
> rs'
PAP MDE Cohen's d = 0.246  →  ≈ $    1847

. 
. file open _f using "_stata_lalonde_outputs_v5.2/artifacts/pap.json", write re
> place

