. * 3c. SMD + t 检验 (skill §3b)
. di as text _n "Standardized Mean Differences (|SMD|<0.1 = balanced):"

Standardized Mean Differences (|SMD|<0.1 = balanced):

. foreach v in age educ black hispan married nodegree re74 re75 {
  2.     qui sum `v' if treat == 1
  3.     local m1 = r(mean)
  4.     local sd1 = r(sd)
  5.     qui sum `v' if treat == 0
  6.     local m0 = r(mean)
  7.     local sd0 = r(sd)
  8.     local smd = (`m1' - `m0') / sqrt((`sd1'^2 + `sd0'^2)/2)
  9.     qui ttest `v', by(treat)
 10.     di as text "  `v': diff=" %9.3f (`m1'-`m0') "  SMD=" %7.3f `smd' "  p=
> " %6.4f r(p)
 11. }
