. if _rc == 0 {
.     test [m_black_mean]treat = [m_other_mean]treat

 ( 1)  [m_black_mean]treat - [m_other_mean]treat = 0

           chi2(  1) =    0.08
         Prob > chi2 =    0.7842
.     di as text "Wald p-value for black vs non-black equality: " %6.4f r(p)
